{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_13","type":"agent_message","text":"The first and third fixes are straightforward: remove an over-specific `part_of` from uvea, and reclassify `scale circulus` away from the immaterial line parent. I’m taking a closer look at the right material parent for `future brain vesicle`, since that is the only modeling choice with some latitude."}}
